<br>
I personally like the idea of putting Ragefire at the end of Veeshan's Peak and making it a triggered event. This would accomplish 2 things. First, it will motivate more players to use that presently under-used zone. Second, it would guarantee that clerics with well raid-capable guilds would be the only ones achieving the epic. It'd truly become a prestige item as originally intended.<br>
